title: Timmy Thomas - Gotta Give a Little Love [Vinyl & Singles]
description:
Recorded on a Technics SL-D2 at 16-bit/44.1khz. 24-bit/96khz forthcoming with the right equipment. Featured in the movie Bachelor Party.

Includes:

* Album
* 45 Single (with Same Ole Song)
* 33 Single (Long & Dub Version)

Hope everyone enjoys this. As far as I know, this album was only available on the Internet as a 128 kbps MP3 release until now (the singles were never available). Thanks to Timmy Thomas for recording such a wonderful song. Special thanks to hoknes, who found the music video on an old VHS tape of New York Hot Tracks
